{"tid":2023511,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【正視聽】國家不可能被摧毀（除非核彈夷平並且殺盡所有人），只有政府可以被摧毀","createTime":"2020-05-19T05:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T05:56:14.000Z","uid":48040,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"21dcd0db4459d26d4bcbb4cda82ed677a694c6f5","tid":2023511,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:09:36.000Z","msg":"林鄭錯誤引用所謂曼德拉的話，話「教育的崩壞會摧毀國家」。<br />\n所謂「摧毀國家」其實係邏輯上不成立。<br />\n國家點摧毀呢？只可以靠核彈，將整個領土完全夷平，然後殺盡每一個國民，咁先為「摧毀國家」。<br />\n所以，林鄭意思其實係，教育如果未能成功令人民洗腦，就會摧毀中共政府。<br />\n<br />\n同樣道理，《國家安全法》其實係《政府安全法》。《國歌法》其實係《黨歌法》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n===========<br />\n我和五毛有個打賭<br />\n本Youtube Channel一個月內訂閱者要破一萬（目前4300），需要你支持！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC7YbpoujZlw&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F6ooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=2b60a055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw</a>"},{"pid":"b00b18c0e4588191315bb24745538e2d626a42af","tid":2023511,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"國家唔係一塊土地 唔係一班人民 係一個體制。"},{"pid":"445ac46ad49b837beb8eb5006b62053cb61f2f70","tid":2023511,"uid":48040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b00b18c0e4588191315bb24745538e2d626a42af","tid":2023511,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"國家唔係一塊土地 唔係一班人民 係一個體制。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:15:38.000Z","msg":"所以，國家係政府？"},{"pid":"38ad51cd467cd1736e86a25547a26e0aadeda9cd","tid":2023511,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"445ac46ad49b837beb8eb5006b62053cb61f2f70","tid":2023511,"uid":48040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b00b18c0e4588191315bb24745538e2d626a42af","tid":2023511,"uid":177089,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:11:09.000Z","msg":"國家唔係一塊土地 唔係一班人民 係一個體制。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:15:38.000Z","msg":"